data.title: Rick and Morty
data.meta_description: Where to watch Rick and Morty (2013) starring Justin Roiland, Spencer Grammer, Chris Parnell and directed by Wes Archer.
data.text: An animated series on adult-swim about the infinite adventures of Rick, a genius alcoholic and careless scientist, with his grandson Morty, a 14 year-old anxious boy who is not so smart. Together, they explore the infinite universes; causing mayhem and running into trouble.
